  "title": "Manufacturing Engineer",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities;</p><ul><li><p>Works with Process Engineers to support, coordinate and follow up on all manufacturing/process related activities on shiftly basis</p></li><li><p>Supports Process Engineer in monitoring line performance/quality / yield and disposition of Hold Lots</p></li><li><p>Tracks the Internal troubleshooting Report (ITR) trend and follow up the Abnormality Lot Report (ALR)</p></li><li><p>Supports the Process Engineering on the qualification/evaluation</p></li><li><p>Ensures that the line complies in all the quality procedures/systems set-up by Process Engineers</p></li><li><p>Handle new product introduction / qualification engineering support</p></li><li></li></ul><p>Requirement;</p><ul><li><p>Minimum degree in the related field</p></li></ul>",
